[I am so sorry to hear what you and your daughter have gone through, and what you are now going through with your current pregnacy!Thank you for sharing your experience, which may be taken into consideration by otherstrying to decide about using this treatment., I hope your son will be as happy and healthy as your daughter., Best wishes...]
